%p Dear #{h(@attendee.full_name)},

%p Your registration as #{I18n.t(@attendee.registration_type.title)} priced #{number_to_currency(@attendee.base_price(@now), :locale => :pt)} at #{@attendee.conference.name} was confirmed successfully.

- unless @attendee.courses.empty?
  %p Besides the conference, you also registered for the following courses:
  %ul
    - @attendee.courses.each do |course|
      %li '#{I18n.t(course.full_name)}' priced #{number_to_currency(course.price(@now), :locale => :pt)}

%p If you have any questions, please contact us at #{mail_to AppConfig[:organizer][:email]}

%small [Please do not reply to this e-mail. It was sent from an unmonitored email address]